fulltitle: Ask the King Ep. 80: Jan. 30, 2020 pt2 - Types of Intelligence, Becoming Private, Censoring Myself
title: Ask the King Ep. 80: Jan. 30, 2020 pt2 - Types of Intelligence, Becoming Private, Censoring Myself
description:
Post up your questions for the next episode of Ask the King here: https://thekingofhate.com/forums/topic/5152-ask-the-king-ep-81-march-26-2020/

Topics in this part:
00:40 Thoughts on load times becoming nearly nonexistent on the next-gen consoles?
2:55 Will I give FF7 a fair shake if they really flesh out the story in the remake?
7:00 Advice for living on your own for the first time?
10:50 Thoughts on people who said you are an "intelligent student" or "stupid student" dependent on GPA?
17:02 What were some of the reasons I was so open when I started on YouTube? How is that different from my life now? If the detractors weren't so bad, would I have shared more even now?
28:05 Thoughts on Mixer as a streaming service and would I ever move to it?
35:25 Patron should-outs
36:15 How do I handle the constant Criticism that I receive?
41:32 Do I still enjoy streaming every day?
42:13 You seem to censor yourself in the modern day. Did you really become more liberal or are you trying to please Twitch?
47:20 Thoughts on Sony not attending E3 again and what is the future of the event?

And then, live stream questions.
